description: With an emphasis on benefiting the community, the environmentally friendly FUEL Mobile Kitchen is feeding the people of Portland incredible locally-sourced cuisine. Their delicious selection of organic comfort food includes sliders with all-natural beef, chicken, and scrumptious veggies. You’ll also find favorites like Crispy Mac & Cheese Bites with Tillamook Aged White Cheddar & fire-roasted green chiles, as well as Hand Cut Fries with salt & cracked black pepper. For all this and much more, make your way to FUEL Mobile Kitchen, it’s an all around feel-good experience.
name: FUEL Mobile Kitchen
